<table><tr><td>National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE). Dyspepsia and gastro-oesophageal reflux disease. Investigation and management of dyspepsia, symptoms suggestive of gastro-oesophageal reflux disease, or both. London (UK): National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE); 2014 Sep. 43 p.&nbsp;(Clinical guideline; no. 184).&nbsp;</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712202151/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=48563&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fwww.nice.org.uk%252fguidance%252fcg184">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712202151im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
