 (041.86), <a href="/web/20180712202151/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0030924&amp;fLockTerm=Peptic+ulcer+of+unspecified+site%2c+unspecified+as+acute+or+chronic%2c+without+mention+of+hemorrhage+or+perforation%2c+without+mention+of+obstruction">Peptic ulcer of unspecified site, unspecified as acute or chronic, without mention of hemorrhage or perforation, without mention of obstruction</a>
