                    <p><div class="content_para"><p><em>Guideline Development Group Members</em>: Peter Barry (<em>Chair</em>), Consultant in Paediatric Intensive Care, Leicester Royal Infirmary; Hugh Barr, Consultant General and Upper Gastrointestinal Surgeon, Gloucestershire Royal Hospital; John de Caestecker, Consultant Gastroenterologist, University Hospitals of Leicester; Mark Follows, Freelance GP, Yorkshire; Alex Ford, Consultant Gastroenterologist, Leeds Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust; Janusz Jankowski, Consultant Gastroenterologist, Leicester Royal Infirmary; Ann Harding, Patient and carer member; Mimi McCord, Patient and carer member</p></div></p>
